"CROSS_SELL_ACCIDENT_ABOUT" = "Hedvigs accident insurance is the ultimate cover for you and your family in case of an accident. Lots of injuries happen outside your home so the coverage applies to all co-insured, no matter what time or where you might find yourself at the moment. You only pay one bill but the insurance applies to everyone who lives under the same roof.\n\nIt’s a no-deductible insurance that compensates you for hospital stays, dental injuries, rehabilitation, therapy and scarring among other things. But also covers more permanent injuries that affect your work and quality of life.";
"CROSS_SELL_ACCIDENT_DESCRIPTION" = "No loopholes on our part. No worries on your part.";
"CROSS_SELL_ACCIDENT_TITLE" = "Accident Insurance";
"CROSS_SELL_CAR_ABOUT" = "A car insurance policy without all the hassle. Comprehensive protection coupled with five-star support from your personal service team.\n\nChoose between traffic insurance, partial, or full coverage. If you change your mind, you can always upgrade or downgrade your protection, or cancel it completely, in the app.\n\nHedvig’s car insurance covers damage caused by you to other people’s property; wildlife accidents; fire damage; burglaries; stone chips; and other unforeseen damages to your car. Crisis counseling and legal protection are also included.";
"CROSS_SELL_CAR_DESCRIPTION" = "For you and your car";
"CROSS_SELL_CAR_TITLE" = "Car insurance";
"CROSS_SELL_HOME_ABOUT" = "Hedvig is everything you’ve ever wished an insurance company could be. Forget paperwork, waiting on hold, and contracts with lock-in clauses. With Hedvig, you have instant access to everything you need, right in the app — from filing claims to adding coverage or canceling your insurance. If an accident happens, expect five-star service and near-instant payouts. Join the over 100,000 others who have already switched to Hedvig — and see for yourself why we’re Sweden’s highest-rated insurer.";
"CROSS_SELL_HOME_DESCRIPTION" = "For you, your family and your home";
"CROSS_SELL_HOME_TITLE" = "Home Insurance";
"CROSS_SELL_PET_ABOUT" = "Hedvig's pet insurance is designed for you and your pet. Personal service, free digital appointments, and a annual health checkup for your pet at no additional costs.";
"CROSS_SELL_PET_DESCRIPTION" = "For your dog or cat";
"CROSS_SELL_PET_TITLE" = "Pet Insurance";
