"HC_INSURANCES_TITLE" = "My insurance";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_01" = "You can easily add more insurance policies and add-ons at hedvig.com. As soon as you sign a new policy with Hedvig, it will appear [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances) in the app. Read more about our insurances [here](https://www.hedvig.com/se-en/insurances).\n \nDo you prefer to sign by phone? Call us on +46 10-45 99 200 on weekdays between 9-16.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_02" = "You can easily change your address directly in the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the relevant insurance policy, then tap Change your information and then Change your address.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_03" = "We have no binding times, so you can cancel your insurance policies whenever you want. The easiest way to cancel a policy is through the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the policy you want to cancel, and then click 'Cancel insurance'.\n\nAdd-ons can be removed from the home insurance on its renewal date. The renewal date is stated in your insurance letter, which you can find under 'Insurance documents'. \n\nYou only pay for the days your insurance is active. If you cancel your policy in the middle of the month, we will charge you for the days up until the cancellation date.\n\nDo you have more questions regarding cancellation? Send us a message here in the app.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_04" = "If you move, or if someone moves in with you, we need to get information from you to keep you covered. You can add co-insured or change your address directly here in the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the policy you want to change and tap the Edit info.\n\nDo you have more questions? Send us a message here in the app.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_05" = "Want to change address or edit your co-insured? You can do it directly in the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the policy you want to edit and tap 'Edit your information'. You can also [upgrade your coverage](https://hedvig.page.link/change-tier) or [add addons](https://hedvig.page.link/travel-addon) directly in the app.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_06" = "Do you want to change address or edit your co-insured? Do it directly here in the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the policy you want to edit and tap the Edit your information.\n\nDo you want to sign up for more insurance policies? \nThe easiest and quickest way to sign up for a new insurance policy is to go to [hedvig.com](https://www.hedvig.com/se-en/insurances).\n\nIf you want to change something else, send us a message here in the app.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_07" = "As an insurance company, Hedvig is obliged to keep the insurance contract and related information for as long as it is possible to make a claim for insurance compensation. This period may vary depending on the type of insurance but is at least 10 years after the expiry of the insurance based on limitation periods.\n\nThese rules affect the possibility to delete an account, as described below.\n\nIf you have an active policy with us, we cannot delete your account. If you want to cancel your insurance, you can do so [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), then select the policy you want to cancel and click on Cancel insurance.\n\nIf you have an open claim, we recommend keeping your account active until your claim is closed. To track of the status of your claim and get messages from our service team, please keep the Hedvig app on your phone.\n\nIf you have cancelled your insurance with Hedvig, we are obliged to save your insurance contract and related information (e.g. registered claims) for at least 10 years after the cancellation of the insurance.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_08" = "If you need to make a claim, you can do so directly here in the app. You can also email your claim to claims@hedvig.com. Describe what happened, what you are seeking compensation for, where it happened, and include your name and full social security number.\n\nFor other questions, it is easiest to write to us here in the app. You can also reach us by phone on +46 10-45 99 200 during weekdays 9-16. Unfortunately, we cannot handle personal information or answer details about a claim over the phone.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_09" = "We have no binding times, so you can cancel your insurance policies whenever you want. The easiest way to cancel a policy is through the app. Click [here](https://hedvig.page.link/insurances), select the policy you want to cancel, and then click 'Cancel insurance'.\n\nAdd-ons can be removed from the home insurance on its renewal date. The renewal date is stated on your insurance letter, which you can find under 'Insurance documents'.\n\nYou only pay for the days that your insurance is active. If you cancel your policy in the middle of the month, we will charge you for the days up until the cancellation date.\n\nDo you have more questions regarding cancellation? Send us a message here in the app.";
"HC_INSURANCE_A_10" = "Make sure that you have entered the discount code correctly. If the discount code still doesn't work, the offer might be expired. If the discount code doesn't work as it should, send us a message here in the app.";
