"SUBMIT_CLAIM_CAR_REPORT_CLAIM_QA_TITLE" = "Questions and answers";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_CAR_REPORT_CLAIM_TEXT" = "We are committed to making the process as swift and seamless as possible for you. The more information you can provide, the quicker we can assist you. Once we have all the necessary details, we will contact you via email.\n\nPlease note that for this matter, you cannot reach us through the app. After reporting the claim, all communication will take place via email.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_CAR_REPORT_CLAIM_TITLE" = "Report your claim";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_CAR_TITLE" = "Car claim";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_COST_LABEL" = "Calling Hedvig Global Assistance is always free of charge. If the help you receive on site is covered by the terms and conditions, you will receive compensation without having to pay a deductible.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_COST_TITLE" = "What does it cost?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ1_LABEL" = "The call is free of charge as long as you have been in an accident, are affected by acute illness or acute dental problems. See your full terms and conditions regarding deductibles and coverage. If you need advice regarding basic healthcare, please call 1177 Healthcare Guide at +46 771-11 77 00.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ1_TITLE" = "What does it cost?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ2_LABEL" = "Hedvig Global Assistance (SOS International) serves as Hedvig's emergency center for acute illnesses, accidents, and emergencies that occur while you are abroad. If you reach out to them, you can receive various forms of support, such as recommendations for the nearest doctor's office, assistance in rebooking flights if necessary, and even obtain a doctor's prescription. If you are traveling and require medical care or assistance, it is essential to contact them as soon as possible.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ2_TITLE" = "Who are Hedvig Global Assistance?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ3_LABEL" = "Contact Hedvig Global Assistance (SOS International) as soon as you can for medical assistance and more information, they can determine what help and compensation you may be entitled to. Remember that you need to see a doctor on site and/or contact Hedvig Global Assistance for the insurance to be valid.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ3_TITLE" = "I am too sick to go to a doctor. What do I do?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ4_LABEL" = "If it is an unexpected and sudden change in your health condition or an accident for which you need medical attention, it is generally considered acute. To provide a more accurate response, we need to examine your particular claim.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ4_TITLE" = "How do I know if it counts as acute or not?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ5_LABEL" = "Contact Hedvig Global Assistance (SOS International) as soon as you can for medical assistance and further information. They can determine if you are eligible for compensation for a new journey home and, if so, assist you in booking it. Remember that approval in advance by SOS International or Hedvig is required for you to be eligible for compensation for the new journey.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ5_TITLE" = "I cannot fly home as planned, what do I do?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ6_LABEL" = "The insurance cannot compensate you for specific activities, excursions, or expenses that you haven't utilized. However, if you have been admitted to the hospital, prescribed indoor bed rest by an on-site doctor, or have to return home prematurely (subject to prior approval by SOS International or Hedvig), you are entitled to a lump sum compensation of 500 SEK per day for unused travel expenses. You can apply for this retroactively, directly through Hedvig.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ6_TITLE" = "I will miss a prebooked activity due to my illness. Is that covered?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_FAQ_LABEL" = "";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_GLOBAL_ASSISTANCE_LABEL" = "Get help to find a hospital or guidance to the medical care you need, wherever you are.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_GLOBAL_ASSISTANCE_TITLE" = "Global Assistance";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_HOSPITAL_LABEL" = "";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_INFO_LABEL" = "Always call your local emergency number if you or someone else is in serious danger";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_INSURANCE_COVER_LABEL" = "We cover costs due to acute illness, injury and acute dental injury abroad. If you are seriously ill and require emergency medical care, contact Hedvig Global Assistance immediately.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_INSURANCE_COVER_TITLE" = "What your insurance covers";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_REBOOK_FLIGHT_LABEL" = "";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_EMERGENCY_TITLE" = "Are you on a trip and need urgent medical care or assistance?";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_GLASS_DAMAGE_HOW_BOOK_LABEL" = "We collaborate with many different workshops across the country. You can easily book your repair online with one of our online partners. If you would rather call your workshop to book an appointment, you need to state that you have car insurance with Hedvig and in some cases you also need the company code \"02301\".";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_GLASS_DAMAGE_HOW_IT_WORKS_LABEL" = "Get started quickly by contacting a workshop. We cooperate with Carglass and Ryds Bilglas, which are located all over the country.\n\nBut of course you can choose another workshop that suits you.";
"SUBMIT_CLAIM_GLASS_DAMAGE_INFO_BUTTON_TEXT" = "We collaborate with both Ryds Bilglas and Carglass to ensure that you receive assistance with your glass damage as quickly as possible.";
